## Line Awesome icon pack

In **WP admin  Voxel  Settings ** **Other**, you can choose to enable the **Line awesome** icon pack.

You can view available icons [here](https://icons8.com/line-awesome)

Once enabled, this pack is made available in various icon picker controls both in back-end and Elementor.

Note: Loading icon packs may impact site performance
